# ISS-015
# Title:      FastAPI int Query() params arrive as str in cross-arch pydantic-core sandbox
# Status:     RESOLVED
# Milestone:  M6
# Discovered: 2026-03-27
# Symptoms:   GET /feeds?offset=1 triggers TypeError in mock_feed_repository.py:
#             "can only concatenate str (not 'int') to str" on list slice operation.
# Root cause: pydantic-core cross-arch stub cannot coerce query-string values from
#             str to int; default values (Python int literals) are unaffected.
# Fix:        Added explicit int() casts before forwarding params to the repository:
#             repo.list(limit=int(limit), offset=int(offset), correlation_id=corr)
# Lesson:     See LL-010

