# ISS-023
# Title:      MockParityRepository.list() signature extended to keyword-only with filters
# Status:     RESOLVED (M10)
# Milestone:  M10
# Discovered: 2026-03-27
# Symptoms:   ParityRepositoryInterface.list() had positional correlation_id only (M8).
#             M10 needed severity/instrument/feed_id filtering.
# Fix:        Changed list() signature to keyword-only:
#             list(*, severity="", instrument="", feed_id="", correlation_id).
#             Existing callers using repo.list(correlation_id=corr) are fully compatible.
# Lesson:     Use keyword-only parameters (*) for all repository list() methods from the start
#             so that adding optional filter args later never breaks existing callers.

